    "description": "需要更好的自控力和更少的干扰？让《Focus Plant时间花园》来帮助你吧！<br><br><strong>《Focus Plant时间花园》是一款游戏化的专注计时器</strong>，旨在帮助你管理时间并专注于生活中重要的事情。<br><br>通过将你的专注时间变成雨滴和种植可爱的植物来改变贫瘠的景观。这些神奇的植物将帮助你管理时间并专注于真正重要的事情。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >保持专注</h2>战胜数字成瘾并保持专注。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150410/extras/ea4ed611a14b6bb2933f83fb3095a1fa.avif?t=1746073617\" width=616 height=346 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >培育植物</h2>利用你的专注时间发现和种植可爱的植物。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150410/extras/8dddf7a8a6497a1a7ded8338d06a8d79.avif?t=1746073617\" width=616 height=346 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多种专注模式</h2>可选择番茄工作法计时器、秒表计时器、倒计时器或小组专注模式。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150410/extras/898a8be86818f59d538c1f7105dbe272.avif?t=1746073617\" width=616 height=346 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >记录</h2>追踪专注时间，以便更好地规划任务。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150410/extras/2c6d1ee6bfb6dbe8fb2abf6f95ee7157.avif?t=1746073617\" width=616 height=346 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >与好友一起玩</h2>与好友一起专注，实现目标。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150410/extras/cdde8d28aa4ef7e68e9e204f373aec2f.avif?t=1746073617\" width=616 height=346 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >装饰</h2>吸引访客并装饰您的花园。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150410/extras/9ba3426f4b2f5bc85f3bda991bbb0d78.avif?t=1746073617\" width=616 height=346 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150410/extras/1a62cea614deb13c3dc122bd8f4ae6c8.avif?t=1746073617\" width=616 height=347 /></span>",
